<%- include("partials/header", { pageTitle: "About" }) %>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
</head>
    <body class="about-body">
        <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
        <main class="about-page">
            <section class="about-hero">
                 <div class="about-hero-bg">
                    <img src="/images/about-hero.png" alt="Luxury retreat cabin">
                </div>
                <div class="about-hero-overlay"></div>
                <div class="about-hero-content">
                    <h1>We didn't set out<br>to build a company.</h1>
                    <p>
                        We set out to find
                        a place to breathe.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="story-section">

                <div class="story-grid">

                <div class="story-copy">

                    <span class="section-label">
                    OUR STORY
                    </span>

                    <h2>
                    This started
                    <br>
                    with a feeling.
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                    It started with a bad weekend.
                    Not dramatic bad. Just the kind
                    of tired that sleep doesn't fix.
                    The kind where you realise
                    you haven't looked at anything
                    beyond your screen in weeks.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                    We booked a place online.
                    It looked beautiful in photos.
                    It was fine.
                    Clean sheets.
                    Fast wifi.
                    A kitchen that smelled like
                    someone else's cooking.
                    </p>

                    <blockquote>
                    “But it didn't feel like anything.”
                    </blockquote>

                </div>

                <div class="story-image">
                    <img src="/images/about-story.jpg">
                </div>

                </div>

            </section>
            <section class="about-philosophy">

                <span class="section-label">
                OUR PHILOSOPHY
                </span>

                <h2>

                A stay should not compete
                for your attention.

                <span>
                    It should create
                </span>

                space for your thoughts
                to return.

                </h2>

            </section>
            <section class="moments-section">

                <div class="moments-top">

                <span class="section-label">
                    THE MOMENTS THAT MATTER
                </span>

                <h2>
                    The feeling
                    was always hidden
                    in the small things.
                </h2>

                </div>

                <div class="moments-grid">

                <div class="moment-card large">
                    <img src="/images/moment1.jpg">
                    <p>
                    Morning coffee
                    with no notifications.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="moment-card">
                    <img src="/images/moment2.jpg">
                    <p>
                    Rain against
                    wooden windows.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="moment-card">
                    <img src="/images/moment3.jpg">
                    <p>
                    Cooking slowly
                    with people you love.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="moment-card wide">
                    <img src="/images/moment4.jpg">
                    <p>
                    Reading while
                    the world outside slows down.
                    </p>
                </div>

                </div>

            </section>
            <section class="about-world">

                <div class="world-dark-overlay"></div>

                <div class="world-content">

                <span class="section-label gold">
                    THE WORLD
                </span>

                <h2>

                    Across forests,
                    coastlines,
                    mountains,
                    and hidden landscapes —

                    <em>
                    we kept finding
                    the same thing.
                    </em>

                </h2>

                <p>
                    People searching
                    for stillness.
                </p>

                </div>

                <img
                src="/images/world-map-glow.png"
                class="world-map-dark">

            </section>
            <section class="belief-section">

                <span class="section-label">
                WHAT WE BELIEVE
                </span>

                <div class="belief-grid">

                <div class="belief-card">

                    <h3>
                    We believe luxury
                    is not excess.
                    </h3>

                    <p>
                    It is silence.
                    Space.
                    Light.
                    Time.
                    </p>

                </div>

                <div class="belief-divider"></div>

                <div class="belief-card">

                    <h3>
                    The best homes
                    don't try too hard.
                    </h3>

                    <p>
                    Neither do the people
                    inside them.
                    </p>

                </div>

                </div>

            </section>
            <section class="team-story">

                <div class="team-story-inner">

                <span class="section-label">
                    WHO WE ARE
                </span>

                <h2>
                    Embarrassingly small
                    for a tech company.
                </h2>

                <p>
                    There are five of us.
                    We argue about everything —
                    which properties deserve
                    a second visit,
                    whether bad lighting ruins a room,
                    and how many throw pillows
                    is too many throw pillows.
                </p>

                <p>
                    We agree on one thing:
                    the places we list should make
                    people feel something they didn't
                    expect to feel on a holiday.
                </p>

                <blockquote>
                    “We've stopped calling it travel.
                    We call it returning.”
                </blockquote>

                </div>

            </section>
            <section class="promise-section">

                <div class="promise-inner">

                <span class="section-label">
                    OUR PROMISE
                </span>

                <h2>
                    Every stay comes
                    with our word.
                </h2>

                <p>
                    If you arrive and it doesn't
                    feel the way we described —
                    the light,
                    the quiet,
                    the host,
                    the whole thing —
                    tell us.
                </p>

                <p>
                    We'll fix it or refund it.
                    No screenshots.
                    No case numbers.
                </p>

                <blockquote>
                    “We'd rather lose money
                    than lose your trust.”
                </blockquote>

                </div>

            </section>
            <section class="about-ending">

                <video
                autoplay
                muted
                loop
                playsinline
                class="ending-video">

                <source src="/videos/about-ending.mp4" type="video/mp4">

                </video>

                <div class="ending-overlay"></div>

                <div class="ending-content">

                <h2>
                    Maybe the best journeys
                    are not about escaping life.
                </h2>

                <p>
                    Maybe they are about
                    returning to it differently.
                </p>

                <a href="/explore">
                    Explore Stays →
                </a>

                </div>

            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </body>
</html>